examples.en: I withdrew my foot a little.
Claudia withdrew her hand from his.
We withdrew to the garden for a private talk.
He withdrew in silent protest before the vote.
England withdrew from any active interference in the struggles of the Continent.
She withdrew $200 from her checking account.
The company withdrew their offer of employment.
She withdrew a document from her briefcase.
The prosecutor withdrew her question to the witness.
US forces withdrew after suffering heavy losses (=many deaths).
Later, the witness who had testified against Muawad withdrew his allegation.
Myers finally bowed to the inevitable (=accepted something he could not change) and withdrew from the campaign.
